legal regulations for the protection of minors provided for the establishment of independent 
judicial bodies and the adoption of protective measures to promote the rehabilitation and 
social reintegration of minors. Pursuant to the Code of Criminal Procedure adopted in 2010, 
the National Committee on Education and Vocational Training in Prisons had been 
